                            <span>(hover each Disaster Type Symbol for each description)</span>
                        </div>  
                        <div class="disaster-type">
                            <ul>
                                <li><input type="checkbox"><img src="public/images/disasters/earthquake.png" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Earthquake"></li>
